Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.44,0:00:04.94,STAFF,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}翻譯：傻瓜三世 ZERO 逆火 校對：傻瓜三世\N\N後期：Misaki喵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.56,0:00:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}老師 打擾一下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.35,0:00:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.23,0:00:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小淵澤
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.24,0:00:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我奶奶嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.32,0:00:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 你趕快回家一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.70,0:00:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我奶奶怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.33,0:00:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.71,0:00:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一切彷彿像作夢一般
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.13,0:00:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}咦 為什麼醒不來呢 怎麼都醒不來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.51,0:00:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}夢好像永遠都不會結束
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.77,0:00:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}現在 我依然在這個夢中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.03,0:00:57.03,Title,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\pos(638,298)}比宇宙更遙遠的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.03,0:00:57.03,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康儷中黑\bord0\b0\fs20\1c&HA6A7AC&\pos(474,626)}喜歡!　 4 5次
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.03,0:00:57.03,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康儷粗黑\bord0\b0\fs20\1c&HA6A7AC&\pos(476,698)}回覆　　2 7條
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.03,0:00:57.03,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康儷中黑\bord0\b0\fs25\1c&HB89E7E&\pos(660,625)}#致親愛的媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.49,0:00:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}三星期？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.87,0:01:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}雖然不算遠 但那裡不能搭直升機過去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.04,0:01:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}難道說
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.04,0:01:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要坐雪地車嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.21,0:01:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.16,0:01:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}耶 終於能坐了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.50,0:01:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這可不是值得開心的事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.38,0:01:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}雪地車很慢的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.84,0:01:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還要避開冰縫等危險地帶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.09,0:01:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只能一下走這邊 一下又換個方向
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.26,0:01:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}佳苗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.97,0:01:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我沒不小心 是故意這麼剪的！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.22,0:01:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嫌頭髮太長很煩的是小吟你呀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.85,0:01:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}反正比貴子剪的好多了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.60,0:01:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你要怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.95,0:01:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這樣好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.78,0:01:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是可以 才請你一起去的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.20,0:01:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我可以…花點時間考慮一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.00,0:01:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.09,0:01:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我以為她會喊著「要去！」就撲過來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.60,0:02:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這個臭氧層破洞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.35,0:02:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是這裡負責觀測的隊員發現
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.27,0:02:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}並率先報告給全世界的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.98,0:02:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這種觀測會使用這種高層氣象觀測氣球
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.98,0:02:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}每天兩次在世界各地同時釋放
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.86,0:02:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}3 2 1 釋放氣球
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.46,0:02:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}報瀨沒有來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.25,0:02:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她想一個人想些事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.34,0:02:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}隊長跟她聊過後 她就不怎麼說話了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.23,0:02:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.64,0:02:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們在這個點上與她失去了聯繫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.61,0:02:57.24,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康粗圓體\bord0\fs35\1c&HD2CAC3&\pos(412,154)\frz40.5}收件者：{\1c&HA29F93&}媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.61,0:02:57.24,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康粗圓體\bord0\fs35\1c&HC3C0B4&\frz40.5\pos(596,256)}主旨：{\1c&H797B76&}致親愛的媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.61,0:02:57.24,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康中特圓體\bord0\b0\fs35\1c&H414945&\pos(386,686)\frz42.81}來自我的myPhone
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.86,0:03:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}山頂茶屋復活啦 有啤酒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.95,0:03:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.49,0:03:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}請用
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.87,0:03:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}已經冰鎮好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.87,0:03:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真機靈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.20,0:03:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.00,0:03:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.21,0:03:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒什麼 覺得拍攝結束了就…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.05,0:03:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.01,0:03:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今天真暖和啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.51,0:03:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.43,0:03:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}現在可是盛夏 今天算冷的了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.60,0:03:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.31,0:03:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}剛才放氣球了 你在這裡看到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.65,0:03:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.07,0:03:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今天的點心好像是紅豆麵包
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.20,0:03:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.03,0:03:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.66,0:03:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只是 那個怎麼說呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.59,0:03:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.75,0:03:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我還想問你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.01,0:04:02.51,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康粗圓體\bord0\fs25\1c&H7B8084&\frz358.5\pos(640,106)}今天的菜單
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.01,0:04:02.51,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康粗圓體\bord0\fs25\1c&H8177D9&\frz23.28\pos(410,70)}特別
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.01,0:04:02.51,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康粗圓體\bord0\fs25\1c&H868D8C&\pos(820,142)}DE送行會！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.01,0:04:02.51,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康粗圓體\bord0\fs25\1c&H666765&\frz2.782\pos(514,464)}蔬菜也要好好吃！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.01,0:04:02.51,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康粗圓體\bord0\fs25\1c&H666765&\pos(914,438)\frz5.631}還有啤酒喝{\i1}！{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.38,0:04:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你問我媽媽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.72,0:04:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小理做事太沒計劃 才搞得這麼複雜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.14,0:04:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你怎麼想到主動請纓問報瀨的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.06,0:04:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.85,0:04:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.52,0:04:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我沒有消沉和煩惱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.57,0:04:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只是覺得普通
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.32,0:04:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有點普通過頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.74,0:04:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}普通？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.24,0:04:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我一直覺得自己來了南極會大哭一場
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.54,0:04:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}「這就是媽媽看過的景色啊」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.83,0:04:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}「媽媽是感動於這片景色
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.50,0:04:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}覺得這裡很美 所以她才想來一趟的啊」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.92,0:04:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我幻想自己會這樣感嘆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.18,0:04:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但實際上完全不是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.10,0:04:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}甚至覺得一切都跟照片上一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.81,0:05:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我記得剛到的時候 你第一句話就是「活該」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.28,0:05:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.19,0:05:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你都忘記了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.57,0:05:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但你是因為媽媽在等你才來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.58,0:05:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為媽媽來過 才想說自己也要來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.58,0:05:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.46,0:05:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以才不斷拜託佳苗小姐她們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.25,0:05:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還打工賺錢 費盡心思就想來這裡一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.96,0:05:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.84,0:05:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}報瀨你說過的 媽媽在這裡等著
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.09,0:05:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小理
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.89,0:05:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你這樣說 報瀨就太可憐了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.35,0:05:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我都知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.48,0:05:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}自己是為了什麼來到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.69,0:05:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.27,0:05:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.36,0:05:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是到那裡後就是盡頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.53,0:05:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一切就結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.66,0:05:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果到了那裡 依然沒有變化
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.78,0:05:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我肯定…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.41,0:05:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一輩子都會是現在的心情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.88,0:06:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在遠征大陸前 我想為南極挑戰及民間南極觀測
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.30,0:06:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}發表30分鐘左右的演講
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.60,0:06:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我要冷死了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.51,0:06:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}啤酒要結冰了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.56,0:06:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}開個玩笑啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.72,0:06:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我想說的只有簡單的一句話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.52,0:06:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小吟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.23,0:06:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們要出發了 乾杯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.44,0:06:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}乾杯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.53,0:06:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這個烤好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.28,0:06:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好冰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.03,0:06:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要是不快點吃 很快就會變成冷肉的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.03,0:06:33.53,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我好忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.58,0:06:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這就是南極燒烤最有趣的一點了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.87,0:06:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}棉花糖掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.12,0:06:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你湊太近了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.54,0:06:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我聽說小淵澤還在猶豫去不去？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.13,0:06:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.17,0:06:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你們真就不管她了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.22,0:06:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}多管閒事不是體貼人 有時不管也是種體貼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.14,0:07:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}又亂編名言了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.48,0:07:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這就是我們大致得出的結論
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.73,0:07:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真羨慕你們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.53,0:07:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}能給彼此空間 說明你們感情很要好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.66,0:07:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你搞什麼鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.29,0:07:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她說我們是好朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.38,0:07:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.76,0:07:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們是好朋友啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.64,0:07:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你不去吃燒烤嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.64,0:07:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你也知道我不喜歡太熱鬧的場合
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.36,0:07:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你是怎麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.94,0:07:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.07,0:07:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我媽媽的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.53,0:07:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這種問題都要問我的話 那我勸你別去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.05,0:08:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不論你有多麼不願意相信
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.55,0:08:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}貴子去世的事實也不會改變
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.22,0:08:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}雖然我們說是繼承她的遺志 生前的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.35,0:08:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但沒人知道 這是否是她的真心想法與願望
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.23,0:08:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那為什麼又要來南極一趟呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.77,0:08:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為我想來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.65,0:08:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我自私地認為 貴子希望我這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.74,0:08:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}說到底 人只會為自己的信念而行動
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.20,0:08:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但只有信念 才能讓人在現實中披荊斬棘
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.67,0:08:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}化不可能為可能 推動自己前進
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.26,0:08:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這是我的理解
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.34,0:08:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你是說 我不該順著別人的想法做事？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.10,0:08:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒錯 不過
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.02,0:09:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你不就是這麼走過來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.73,0:09:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}搬家工
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.90,0:09:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}收銀員
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.74,0:09:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}清掃工
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.08,0:09:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}清掃工
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.75,0:09:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}送報紙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.46,0:09:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我知道自己是在強人所難
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.54,0:09:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}收銀員
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.59,0:09:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}搬家工
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.80,0:09:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}交通量調查
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.01,0:09:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}清掃工
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.01,0:09:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}工廠
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.97,0:09:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}工廠
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.89,0:09:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}收銀員
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.68,0:09:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}快遞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.85,0:09:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是我無論如何都想去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.35,0:09:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}收銀員
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.56,0:09:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.52,0:09:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}媽媽在等著我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.99,0:10:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.83,0:10:10.21,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fnGen Jyuu Gothic Bold\bord0\fs45\1c&H8C85D2&\frz8.085\frx356\fry346\pos(316,458)}加油{\fsp-15}！！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.21,0:10:10.88,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fnGen Jyuu Gothic Bold\bord0\fs65\1c&HA98CCE&\frx356\fry346\frz351\move(378,112,188,-72,0,633)}加油{\fsp-15}！！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.04,0:10:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對吧 這可是手工的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.79,0:10:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}聽說內陸之旅也要帶著這個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.22,0:10:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那是你的行李？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.80,0:10:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.38,0:10:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}太多了 減半 五分鐘搞定
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.10,0:10:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.06,0:10:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.06,0:10:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.73,0:10:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就這樣 最後的旅途開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.32,0:10:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}朝著距離日本14,000公里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.83,0:10:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}比宇宙更遙遠 恍若天邊的那個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.17,0:10:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}原來不是坐雪地車啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.88,0:11:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這個S-16是我們內陸之旅的起始據點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.64,0:11:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}給停靠此地的雪地車裝貨就是今天的任務
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.39,0:11:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.48,0:11:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這裡比昭和基地要冷多了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.98,0:11:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這裡看到的景色 就很有南極的味道了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.14,0:11:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}確實是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.85,0:11:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好慢！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.23,0:11:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有人有7對的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.31,0:11:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}7對
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.69,0:11:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那就…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.31,0:11:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真有啊！？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.52,0:11:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}居然連續三輪當大貧民…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.24,0:12:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這裡是114 通過S-18
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.45,0:12:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好 112收到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.83,0:12:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.21,0:12:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}工作時間到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.88,0:12:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要到外面去 做好心理準備
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.92,0:12:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好痛 每吸一口氣胸口就好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.55,0:12:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}鼻子都快沒感覺了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.39,0:12:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}接下來隨著海拔提高 還會更冷的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.64,0:12:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.85,0:12:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你還真帶來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.06,0:12:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.56,0:12:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.73,0:12:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒知覺了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.15,0:12:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不快吃就冷掉囉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.78,0:12:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}晚上會把引擎關掉的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.86,0:12:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}燃料可沒多到能一直開著引擎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.08,0:12:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這裡是昭和 這裡是昭和
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.41,0:12:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}內陸組能聽到嗎 請講
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.25,0:12:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}定時聯絡 來練習一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.30,0:13:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為我們都不知道接下來會發生什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.76,0:13:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今晚風勢可能會增強
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.14,0:13:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在車輛間移動一定要抓緊這條繩子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.64,0:13:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就算只有幾公尺也不能大意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.19,0:13:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要是被暴風雪捲走 就回不來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.57,0:13:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.74,0:13:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.32,0:13:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是太陽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.58,0:13:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有點像世界末日到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.91,0:13:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那叫太陽光柱 也就是Sun Pillar
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.42,0:13:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是由冰晶反射產生的光學現象
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.13,0:13:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}媽媽也看到過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.38,0:13:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 她看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.89,0:13:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可以說她站在那裡 看著看著就睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.15,0:14:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.49,0:14:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}難道是暴風雪？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.24,0:14:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是暴風雪來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.41,0:14:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒問題的 只要待在車裡就好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.08,0:14:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什麼都看不到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.62,0:14:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這裡也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.25,0:14:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對喔 你們還是第一次親眼見到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.46,0:14:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.56,0:14:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}媽媽失蹤的時候也是這種情況嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.77,0:14:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}或許是東西忘在內陸基地裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.65,0:14:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也可能是滑了一跤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.74,0:14:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}貴子？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.16,0:14:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等我發現的時候 她已經不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.96,0:15:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒過多久 暴風雪就颳了起來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.72,0:15:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.14,0:15:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}貴子！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.89,0:15:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}非常地…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.64,0:15:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}美呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.02,0:16:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}報瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.48,0:16:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.73,0:16:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}睡不著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.07,0:16:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是 剛剛才睡醒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.07,0:16:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小理喜歡南極嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.20,0:16:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 非常喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.41,0:16:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.46,0:16:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但如果是一個人來 就不知道喜不喜歡了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.67,0:16:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是那樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.67,0:16:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為和大家一起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.84,0:16:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只要大家一起 去北極或許也會一樣喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.60,0:16:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}報瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.35,0:16:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}謝謝你帶我來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.23,0:16:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是你幫我找到了自己的青春
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.86,0:16:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}致親愛的媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.91,0:16:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我交到朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.37,0:17:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一直喜歡當獨行俠的我交到了朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.13,0:17:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}雖然她們有點怪 有點麻煩 還有點廢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.18,0:17:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但卻是陪著我走到了南極的朋友們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.22,0:17:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們吵過架 流過淚 也出過問題
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.60,0:17:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但我們依舊走過長長的旅途 來到了媽媽到過的這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.45,0:17:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為和大家一起 我才走到了這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.91,0:17:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}媽媽 從你那邊能看到什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.92,0:17:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我也能看到 你看過的風景嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.97,0:18:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我很快就會到媽媽在的那個地方的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.19,0:18:14.36,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康超特楷體\bord0\b0\fs25\1c&H353749&\frz2.986\move(718,8,718,262,37,4166)}南極挑戰第一次派遣隊天文觀測站
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.57,0:18:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好久沒來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.94,0:18:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}讓你久等了 雖然還得讓你等一段時間
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.28,0:18:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那樣沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.74,0:18:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不可能沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.62,0:18:31.38,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康超特楷體\bord0\b0\fs30\1c&H353749&\frz10.31\move(546,188,546,496,0,7753)}南極挑戰第一次派遣隊天文觀測站
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.95,0:18:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}接下來要重新打地基 蓋房子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.75,0:18:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}把零件一個個運來 製造望遠鏡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.96,0:18:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}雖然建立小淵澤天文台還要不少時間
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.92,0:18:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.38,0:18:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小淵澤…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.64,0:18:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她肯定是回想起了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.56,0:18:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}和我媽媽一起看這裡時的情景
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.48,0:18:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}報瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.82,0:19:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不可能找到媽媽的東西了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.74,0:19:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}都三年前的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.12,0:19:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那可不好說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.95,0:19:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒錯 換個角度想 這裡有三年沒人來過了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.96,0:19:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好了啦 不用找了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.58,0:19:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不能輕言放棄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.75,0:19:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什麼都行 哪怕就一樣也好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.09,0:19:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}已經可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.84,0:19:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.76,0:19:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}找不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.05,0:19:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼你能這麼斷定？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.68,0:19:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.64,0:19:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}能到這裡就夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.47,0:19:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我已經完成目的了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.48,0:19:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}已經到過媽媽在的地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.94,0:19:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}謝謝你們 所以已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.94,0:19:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不可以 我們都到這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.24,0:19:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}都到這裡了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.32,0:19:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一個也好 我們要找到報瀨媽媽來過這裡的證據
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.83,0:19:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小理
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.37,0:19:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}報瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.42,0:19:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.32,0:20:34.04,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}そっと「会いたい」聞いた
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.75,0:20:42.47,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}空に溶けて消えた
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.34,0:21:00.07,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}今も胸の奥　静かに揺れている
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.23,0:21:07.87,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}白く輝く世界
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.66,0:21:16.17,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}残した足跡も消えて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.17,0:21:24.34,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}果てないと思ってた時が
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.68,0:21:32.56,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}終わりを告げる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.81,0:21:42.40,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}だからずっと忘れない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.57,0:21:51.91,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}言葉より大切な思いが
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.91,0:22:01.09,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}きっと繋いでくれる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.88,0:22:13.10,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}いつの日か　また旅に出よう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.71,0:22:54.26,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\fs40\an3}だからずっと忘れない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.60,0:23:03.94,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\fs40\an3}一緒にいた　かけがえのない時が
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.94,0:23:13.16,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\fs40\an3}きっと繋いでくれる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.87,0:23:24.84,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\fs40\an3}いつまでも　いつまでも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.67,0:23:30.18,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\fs40\an3}またね
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.32,0:20:34.04,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}聽見一聲輕輕的「想見你」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.75,0:20:42.47,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}聲音漸漸消失在了空中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.34,0:21:00.07,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}我的心底依然在暗自動搖
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.23,0:21:07.87,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}雪白閃耀的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.66,0:21:16.17,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}我們踩下的足跡 漸漸褪去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.17,0:21:24.34,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}原以為這些時光 永無止境
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.68,0:21:32.56,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}卻突然畫上了句號
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.81,0:21:42.40,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}所以這份心情 我不會忘懷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.57,0:21:51.91,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}它比任何語言 都要寶貴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.91,0:22:01.09,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}總有一天 會再度牽起你我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.88,0:22:13.10,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}帶著我們 又一次踏上旅途
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.71,0:22:54.26,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\fs40}所以這些時光 我不會忘懷
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.60,0:23:03.94,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\fs40}你我一道 度過的珍貴點滴
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.94,0:23:13.16,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\fs40}想必它們 會永遠牽起你我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.87,0:23:24.84,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\fs40}直到永遠 直到永恆
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.67,0:23:30.18,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\fs40}再見了
